{"label":"Patterns in Mathematics","id":"patterns-6","list":[{"type":"match","id":"match","label":"Match: Number sequence","onlyBigScreen":true,"data":{"title":"Match: Number sequence","actWidth":900,"text":"1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, ... | All 1’s\n1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 7, ... | Counting numbers\n1, 3, 5, 7, 9, 11, 13, ... | Odd numbers\n2, 4, 6, 8, 10, 12, 14, ... | Even numbers\n1, 3, 6, 10, 15, 21, 28, ... | Triangular numbers\n1, 4, 9, 16, 25, 36, 49, ...  | Squares\n1, 8, 27, 64, 125, 216, ... | Cubes\n1, 2, 3, 5, 8, 13, 21, ... | Virahānka numbers (Fibonoci numbers)\n1, 2, 4, 8, 16, 32, 64, ... | Powers of 2\n1, 3, 9, 27, 81, 243, 729, ... | Powers of 3"}},{"type":"match","label":"Match: Pictorial Representation","id":"match-simple-2","onlyBigScreen":true,"data":{"rightImgType":"custom","big":true,"actWidth":1100,"rightSideWidth":"477px","rightSideHeight":["48px","48px","48px","48px","86px","98px","134px"],"title":"Match the pictorial representation of number sequence with their names.","imgPath":"img/math/big/patterns-maths-6","text":"All 1's , all-1s\nCounting Numbers, counting-numbers\nOdd Numbers, odd-numbers\nEven Numbers, even-numbers\nTriangular Numbers, triangular-numbers\nSquares, squares\nCubes, cubes"}},{"type":"dragDropImgLabel","label":"Shape Sequence","id":"monuments-india","onlyBigScreen":true,"data":{"title":"Drag the names and drop on the images.","path":"img/math/big/patterns-maths-6","actWidth":1300,"imgWidth":498,"imgHeight":117,"text":"complete-graphs | Complete Graphs\n        stacked-squares | Stacked Squares\n        stacked-triangles | Stacked Triangles\n        koch-snowflake | Koch Snowflake"}},{"type":"dragDropImgLabel","label":"Sequence of Polygons","id":"polygons","onlyBigScreen":true,"data":{"title":"Sequence of Polygons","path":"img/math/big/patterns-maths-6","actWidth":1000,"imgWidth":200,"imgHeight":170,"text":"triangle | Triangle\nquadrilateral | Quadrilateral\npentagon | Pentagon\nhexagon | Hexagon\nheptagon | Heptagon\noctagon | Oct